title: Planemakers look at higher output to meet demand
text:
Planemakers look at higher output to meet demand 5:32pm GMT - 01:42 
The world's largest planemakers signalled a possible increase in output of their most popular passenger jets on Tuesday, highlighting their confidence about growth in demand for air travel. Kate King reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
